# APIDriftScanner - Time-Based API Performance Tracker

APIDriftScanner watches endpoints and highlights trends in degradation or unexpected performance variation.

## Features
- Drift detection over time  
- HTTP status & latency logging  
- Optional chart output  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_APIDriftScanner.git
cd 33_APIDriftScanner
python monitor.py
